i srcâ‹…content
i srcâ‹…types

Î»all_docs_section(config:srcâ‹…types.SiteBuildConfig,docs:[srcâ‹…types.SitePage])â†’đť•Š=
  "<section class=\"listing\"><h2>Docs</h2><ul class=\"page-list\">"++page_cards(config,docs)++"</ul></section>"

Î»all_specs_section(config:srcâ‹…types.SiteBuildConfig,spec:[srcâ‹…types.SitePage])â†’đť•Š=
