Î»latest_articles(articles:[srcâ‹…types.SitePage],config:srcâ‹…types.SiteBuildConfig)â†’đť•Š=
  "<section class=\"listing\"><h2>Latest Articles</h2><ul class=\"page-list\">"++page_cards(config,srcâ‹…content.take_first(5,articles))++"</ul><p><a href=\""++site_url(config.base_path,"/articles/")++"\" class=\"view-all\">View all articles â†’</a></p></section>"

Î»nav(config:srcâ‹…types.SiteBuildConfig)â†’đť•Š=
